post_content.caption: Trump’s ‘prospects for prevailing’ in getting GA case dismissed are ‘slim to none’
post_content.description:
MSNBC legal correspondent Lisa Rubin, former Georgia federal prosecutor Amy Lee Copeland and former U.S. attorney Harry Litman discuss the Trump team's push to dismiss the Georgia election interference case.
